<div class="support-wrapper">
    <div id="cardAtendimentoPergunta" class="card" style="display: none; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
        <div class="card-header text-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between" style="background-color: {{customcolor}};">
            <h5 class="m-0" style="font-size: 16px;">Atendimento Online</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close closeButtonFirst" style="color:white; border:none; background:none;">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center">
            <p>Olá! Você deseja conversar com um atendente agora?</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-around mt-3">
                <button class="btn try-zammad-chat"
                        style="width: 100px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: {{customcolor}}; color: white; border: none;">Sim</button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-danger noZammadButton" style="width: 100px; border-radius: 8px;">Não</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="cardFormulario" class="card" style="display: none; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
        <div class="card-header text-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between" style="background-color: {{customcolor}};">
            <h5 class="m-0" style="font-size: 16px;">Deixe sua mensagem</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close closeButtonForm" style="color:white; border:none; background:none;">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center">
            <p>Infelizmente não há atendentes online no momento. Gostaria de registrar sua dúvida?</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-around mt-3">
                <button id="feedback-form-try" class="btn"
                        style="width: 100px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: {{customcolor}}; color: white; border: none;">Sim</button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary noZammadButtonForm" style="width: 100px; border-radius: 8px;">Não</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display: none;">
        <button id="feedback-form">Trigger Form</button>
        <button class="open-zammad-chat">Trigger Chat</button>
    </div>
</div>